      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Skip the hardware aisle &mdash; get it done properly.</h2>
        <p>An honest inspection and a treatment plan that actually eliminates the colony. Already sprayed? Tell us what you did &mdash; we work from there.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
